summary:
Backstory:
Liam and Louis had always been a little insecure and suspicious of Harry and Zayn's relationship. Then it happened...
body:
Puppy dog eyes

Backstory:

Liam and Louis had always been a little insecure and suspicious of Harry and Zayn’s relationship. Then it happened one time that both H and Z were awol for a few days. Louis and Liam freaked out. It took several painful weeks for Harry and Zayn to convince their respective boyfriends that nothing was going on.

Fast forward a few years, and this interview took place:

Zayn on the phone to Harry after seeing the interview

Zayn: You tell your buddy Grimmy, he can go suck a lemon. I’d tell him to suck something else but he’d probably enjoy it.

Harry: Z, I’m sorry. I ripped into him after the taping, I promise. Louis wasn’t too happy either.

Zayn: You don’t actually expect me to feel sorry for you, do you? I have to deal with Liam freaking-puppy-dog-eyes Payne. You know, the man who so resembles a puppy that his fans are constantly calling him a puppy. Like, WTF!!!

summary:
Dear Harry, 
It's hard going through life without you. When I was younger, I used to turn to you for laughter, tears, and an...
body:
Dear Harry,
It’s hard going through life without you. When I was younger, I used to turn to you for laughter, tears, and an escape. Now I just can’t seem to do that because you are always on the move. You will always have a special spot in my heart for the feeling of fullness you gave me. I miss you Styles. Much Love!

x m
